{
  "stem": "11723.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And coming from the island to the Buda side, I don't know how my mother got there, but I think she told me that she was hopping from ice to ice.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then she went to the Red Cross to try to see if they know where we were.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Red Cross told her that the house where we were burned down, but that we were alive but they don't know where we are.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she just set out to go from home to home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the second day she got caught in this snowstorm.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And she was walking, and she was very, very tired and she thought that she saw an apparition.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She thought she was these two sleds, and then she recognized the knitted outfit that she knitted for me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she still thought that she was imagining things, and that's when she started running.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And she came in she saw that it was us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But anyway, all night I was talking to her and I was telling her all the things that bothered me and all the things that happened.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I said to her, you know, Mom, I dreamt last night that Mama C-- that's what I called my grandmother on my father's side.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was closer to her because she lived nearer-- that Mama C had a bloody head and she was on the floor and she was yelling and nobody helped her.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my mother said, don't be silly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Mama C is in the sanatorium, and I'm going to go see her tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Your grandmothers are fine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So the next morning, after a breakfast of asparagus, my mother left.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
